      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "**Subject: Updated GDPR Compliance Procedures for the New Marketing Database**\n\nThis memo outlines our enhanced approach to data governance, ensuring we strictly adhere to the **Accountability Principle** by integrating **Privacy by Design** into every stage of the **Data Protection Impact Assessment**. We have clearly defined our roles as **Data Controller** and **Data Processor**, establishing a robust **Processing Basis** that relies on **Consent** and **Legitimate Interest** while enforcing **Data Minimization** to limit the **Special Categories of Data** we collect. Our new framework mandates a strict **Retention Period** aligned with **Storage Limitation** and **Pseudonymisation** standards, ensuring that any **Automated Decision-making** remains transparent and fair. Furthermore, we are committed to full **Transparency** regarding **Cross-border Transfer** mechanisms and will proactively manage **Subject Access Request** and **Right to Portability** to uphold the **Right to Erasure** and timely **Breach Notification** protocols.",
      "source": "target",
